  "title": "Shipping/ Logistics Assistant (Basic $2500-$2800 / Changi)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Shipping/ Logistics Assistant (Freight Forwarding Company) ID9213<br />Location: Changi<br />Working Hours: 9am to 6pm, Mon-Fri & 9am-1pm, Alternate Saturday<br />Basic Salary: $2500-$2800<br />Benefit:<br />-VB/AWS with 7days AL<br /><br />Job Description:<br />-Coordinate air freight shipments from booking to final delivery.<br />-Book airline space, arrange cargo pickup, and track shipment progress.<br />-Prepare shipping documents and ensure compliance with international and IATA regulations.<br />-Communicate with customers, provide updates, and prepare freight quotations.<br />-Work closely with sales and operations teams to improve efficiency and service quality.<br /><br />Requirement:<br />- Min 1 year Shipping Experience</p>",
